SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 13 - The Landwehr Canal DLC
DESCRIPTION:Precision gameplay continues with more stealth, patience, and
 those moments where everything either goes perfectly... or
 catastrophically loud. In the dark days of the end of World War 2 amidst
 the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can change history... Elite sniper Karl
 Fairburne returns to the front line in the remaster of this award-winning
 stealth-action experience. Packed with new features, contemporary visuals
 and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JAeRr2PGsGY
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23302211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260424T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260520T135200Z
DTSTART:20260515T203000Z
DTEND:20260515T223000Z
SUMMARY:Crime Scene Cleaner | Ep. 14 - This Is Getting Worse the Longer I
 Stay
DESCRIPTION:Back on cleanup duty, where every room somehow becomes more
 horrifying after I start cleaning it. The bucket remains loyal. Once you
 get tangled with the mob, you will forever be a part of the mob. At least
 they pay a decent salary and all you have to do is clean up after their
 dirty work, but you know what you're doing. So clean crime scenes, earn as
 much money as you can, and get ready for the next mission.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PRYuQJ89NKU
CATEGORIES:Crime Scene Cleaner
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
