DTEND:20260519T223000Z
SUMMARY:Duck Side of the Moon | Ep. 1 - A Cozy Little Trip to the Moon
DESCRIPTION:Back to our cozy lunar duck adventure! Relaxed vibes, moon
 exploration, and a surprising amount of charm packed into one tiny trip.
 Waddle and fly as a duck in space! Explore every corner of the galaxy and
 find curious creatures and materials along the way. Craft gadgets, upgrade
 your spaceship, and get cozy in this relaxing adventure.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wO7ciJj657Q
CATEGORIES:Duck Side of the Moon
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
