SUMMARY:Crime Scene Cleaner | Ep. 16 - Pretty Sure This Wasn't League Night
DESCRIPTION:Another cleanup job, another deeply suspicious scene. Things
 are getting stranger, messier, and somehow harder to explain. Once you get
 tangled with the mob, you will forever be a part of the mob. At least they
 pay a decent salary and all you have to do is clean up after their dirty
 work, but you know what you're doing. So clean crime scenes, earn as much
 money as you can, and get ready for the next mission.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Crime Scene Cleaner
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
