LAST-MODIFIED:20260520T135200Z
DTSTART:20260523T203000Z
DTEND:20260523T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 48 - I Came for Nuka-Cola, Not This Situation
DESCRIPTION:Nuka-World continues to be the least relaxing \"vacation\"
 destination imaginable. More chaos, more danger, more bad decisions. As
 the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a world destroyed by nuclear
 war. Every second is a fight for survival, and every choice is yours. Only
 you can rebuild and determine the fate of the Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
